frames.caption: A colossal bear towers over a city street, its mouth open in a roar as it strides between skyscrapers. Below, a yellow taxi speeds away, highlighting the surreal scale of the creature against the urban backdrop.
frames.description: The scene is set in a bustling city with towering skyscrapers lining the street. A gigantic bear is depicted in a dynamic pose, seemingly in motion, as it dominates the urban landscape. The presence of the bear creates a sense of chaos and urgency, emphasized by the fleeing taxi.

frames.caption: A gigantic bear towers over a city street, dwarfing the surrounding skyscrapers and vehicles. The scene captures the bear mid-stride, its massive paws dominating the foreground as cars appear tiny in comparison.
frames.description: The image depicts a surreal scene where an enormous bear is walking through a city street. The urban setting is characterized by tall buildings and a few visible vehicles, emphasizing the bear's colossal size.
